{"id":"4478","user":{"id":"224324","nickname":"小无无","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FoXf4RvLE3xDl453bg6-4Cda8dh_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【编程聊天室】第六期——一个数学问题（萌新勿入！）","content":"<p>Hello,累的死and砖头们，我无可又回来啦！（再次重申：我是无可的小号！！！）今天，编程聊天室又再次强势回归啦！</p>\n<p>来，P了张图：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgRRnWWrtg4DFkY9zoIaAej2xGO7\"><br></p>\n<p>这个就当聊天室图标啦~</p>\n<p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/f4/xklzhuanquan_thumb.gif\">无可专用分界线<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/f4/xklzhuanquan_thumb.gif\">~~~~~~~~~~~~~</p>\n<p>今天我们一起来讨论下一个数学问题，</p>\n<p>最近，</p>\n<p>有些人说：</p>\n<p>0.9,9循环=1</p>\n<p>他们的理由是：</p>\n<p>1÷3=0.3,3循环，</p>\n<p>0.3,3循环=3分之1，</p>\n<p>3分之1×3=3分之3=1，</p>\n<p>0.3×3=0.9</p>\n<p>然后由此推出公式：</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;· &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;·</p>\n<p>0.9（你知道这是循环点的）=0.3×3=3分之1×3=3分之3=1</p>\n<p>简便后：</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;·</p>\n<p>0.9=1</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>无可个人对这种想法保持不一致的想法：</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;·</p>\n<p>1÷3并不完全等于0.3，</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ·</p>\n<p>理应是：1÷3≈0.3，</p>\n<p>酱紫说，就不是那回事了。</p>\n<p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/f4/xklzhuanquan_thumb.gif\">无可专用分界线<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/f4/xklzhuanquan_thumb.gif\">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</p>\n<p>大家对这个题目有什么想法呢？</p>\n<p>快快来投稿吧！</p>","board_id":"5","board_name":"你问我答","updated_at":1503813712,"created_at":1498221915,"n_views":266,"n_replies":37,"n_comments":8,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}